Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:04.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:06.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:08.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:09.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I confess, I already have \Na good idea of who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of those \Nso-called "dying messages".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say you're wrong there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be! You're the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:38.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,212)}Sunday Suspense
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:40.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,212)}The Beautiful Rich Great \NYoung Detective Lady Saw It!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:42.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,212)}The Case of the Murdered Female \NTeacher Amidst Clouds of Steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:44.69,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,273)}As a mysterious beauty smiled bewitchingly in a steamy open-air mixed bath,\N it was a night in a ravine quiet of the passion of man and woman, \Nthat a monkey ran off uttering a death cry and wept softly\N at the far ends of love and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:46.56,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(408.,271)}In Cooperation With \NBoonies Hot Springs Tourist Association
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Whosoever commands the butlers, \Ncommands the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:55.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Butler War that will \Nshake up the world has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This episode of "Hayate" \Nis very suspenseful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:01:00.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But as always, please enjoy it \Nwith your whole family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\NI don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai!\NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:13.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\NThe future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:18.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dou yattemo katenai akuma ga\NA demon that I just can't win against
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:23.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Megami no kao o shite chakkari (O_O;)\NBrazenly pretending to be a goddess (O_O;)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:28.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keikenchi ja tannai kurai dakara\NExperience points are almost not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:34.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshou tanren shikou-sakugo ni sessa-takuma\NTraining for life, working hard at trial and error
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:39.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mondai nara muzukashii-hodo ude ga naru shi\NTougher the problem the more it gets me going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:44.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorokobu kao ga mirerya sore de ii shi\NSeeing the joy on your face is enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:50.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu o boku wa te ni ireta\NI've found a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin kimi o tsurete tsuki-susumou!\NTotally free, I'll take you and push forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:59.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Happii na kanchigai\NA happy misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:02.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikai wa yuruganai!\NMy pledge will stand fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:07.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze no yukue mo kaete-miseru\NI'll even change the direction of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakkou wa kini-shinai\NI won't care how I look
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Unmei ja kujikenai!\NNo destiny will discourage me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:18.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano kumo chirasu hayate no gotoku!\NLike the sudden gale scattering the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}The Beautiful Rich Great Young Detective Lady Saw It! The Case of the Murdered Female Teacher Amidst Clouds of Steam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.51,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}Beautiful Rich Great Young Detective Lady\NNagi Sanzenin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The autumn breeze truly is quite pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.89,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}Assistant and Butler\NHayate Ayasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And the autumn leaves are very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad we took the plunge \Nand came for a trip to the hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}Assistant and Maid\NMaria
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Miss, where \Nis the inn we're going to stay at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! How very classic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to enjoy hot springs \Nis to relax quietly at a rustic inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems to be giving off \Na rather ominous aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a very "untouchable" \Natmosphere about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just heard a scream come \Nfrom that inn, didn't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}Waitresses\NThe Student Council Girl Trio
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}Guest in the Next Room\NShiori Makimura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.85,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(225,234)}And Her Lover\NEight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}Corpse\NYukiji Katsura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is different than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'd never get married \Nif I stayed looking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I never expected to get caught up \Nin a murder case at the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a delightful... I mean, \Nwhat a troubling situation this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, we must contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sees through to the one and only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the looks of a snooty softy \Nand the brains of a societal bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Great Detective Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kiddy backpack doesn't \Nlook out of place one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the jab you should be making!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.77,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}The Corpse's Little Sister\NHinagiku Katsura
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought you \Nwere a no-good big sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never imagined you'd end up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my sympathies, \Nbut please try to remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually something \NI'd like for you all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A video...tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just received it \Nearlier by bike messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect it was taped by my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.63,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,First of Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's recording properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's this room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it appears to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, by the time you see this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your big sis may already be \None of the stars in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They put it well when they \Nsaid "beauty dies first".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does she get off saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, never mind that. \NThe background scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to come to this inn \Nby a letter from an unknown sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this person \Nhas a grudge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know who it is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they'll be visiting me \Nhere in this room soon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, I want you to know, \Nif I should end up dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my killer will be the person \Nwho shows up after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you catch the person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sue them for plenty of damages! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where it ends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It got cut off \Nat the most crucial part!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as awful \Nas a mother who tricks her child
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by putting honey on cucumber \Nand says, "Here's some melon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, as awful as saying soy \Nsauce on pudding is sea urchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as awful as putting dried seaweed \Nand soy sauce on mandarin oranges
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,and calling it salmon roe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After killing the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the culprit probably erased the part \Nthat revealed who the murderer is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then sent the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is a challenge \Nissued by the culprit to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I confess, I already have \Na good idea of who the culprit is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm just the guest \Nin the room next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a super low-key character,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who's never appeared since Episode 23...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appeared in Episode 25, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I've even seen through the trick, \Nright slick and lickety-split!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.87,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick #1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You summoned the victim to a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just try laying a hand on me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll make you pay all the bar tabs \Nthat I've accumulated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Bills
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And using a speckled snake \Nthat just happened to be passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snaaaaake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Perfect \Ndetective work, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ask how it was, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, you totally borrowed \Nthe most famous trick in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Sir Doyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught in the act! You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're wrong! I'm not the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not argue with me! Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat my honey like she's a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, it appears the culprit \Nis someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to be honest, \NI had a feeling that it might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which makes you three the suspicious ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.10,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick #2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where in the world am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three summoned the victim to a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and using a giant speckled octopus \Nthat just happened to be passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooooctopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this giant speckled octopus about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, we weren't even in the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, allow yourselves \Nto be arrested without resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are others more likely \Nto have motives, aren't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you have a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who might have the biggest \Ngrudge against the victim would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:16.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd have to be none other \Nthan the butler-in-debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a second! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:24.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't all of you look at me \Nwith such suspicion, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of all the people, \NI trusted you the most, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, I am not the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick #3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the speckled elephant \Nthat just happened to be passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeeelephant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you wouldn't \Nhurt a fly and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, your deductions are nonsense \Nbased on hunches and inspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Yama? I've caught the perp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the scene has \Nswitched somewhere along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:48.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This solves the case, but it won't \Nbring the victim back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from a hot springs inn to Africa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who the heck are you talking to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll talk again on the \Nrooftop, gazing at the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you have to kill me \Nbefore you're satisfied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story's not making any progress here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really embarrassing to be lying \Nhere dressed like this, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to do things \Nproperly, as scripted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.91,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a so-called dying message!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a "dying message"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:27.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A dying message is a hint \Nthat the victim leaves conspicuously
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,right before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:29.84,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheney
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.13,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But "Hibiya"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiya refers to an area close to Ginza,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,which includes Yurakucho, \Nwhich is in Chiyoda Ward, Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:46.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, this is also where Japan's \Nfirst electric traffic signal was set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need such in-depth information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if we can decipher \Nthe meaning of this message,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll know who the culprit is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suddenly becoming more \Nlike a serious mystery now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing compared \Nto the secrets of the pyramids and UFOs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I don't know about this different \Ncharacter with the glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good instinct. \NJust what I'd expect of my assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. This crime was perpetrated \Nby a different character,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is currently not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A different character?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After murdering the victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the culprit ought to be \Nhiding somewhere else now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're \Ngoing to say it's Hibiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take another close look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.99,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look \Nat it, it says "Hibiya".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This message includes \Nthe kaki-no-tane crackers next to it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely. What's written \Nthere are the radicals on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you assume the crackers \Nare the radicals...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.17,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Mixed Bath"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprise! It reads "mixed bath"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a deduction out of left field...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, this inn actually \Nconveniently has a mixed bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is certain to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surely not... No matter how you look at it, \Nthere's no way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And just who might the culprit be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your valuables! Quick! \N({\i1}Ka{\i0}neme no mono o! Haya{\i1}ku{\i0}!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you pay the ward tax? \N({\i1}Ku{\i0}minzei harat{\i1}ta{\i0}?)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flunking Girl Trio's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.51,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flunking Girl Trio Gluttony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.51,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, Like a Dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this eating or a hot springs fan \Nservice scene? Can we clarify that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effects of this hot spring are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rissy, that's after we eat! {\i1}After{\i0} we eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a merry-go-round of tastiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't eaten yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilgamesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, isn't this delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:11.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't you say that the art is different \Nfrom the previous scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria, when \Nin the world did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so you're the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't sweat the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sexy scene is a cliché \Nof suspense drama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,She is using a towel for this shoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:35.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but when you are actually bathing, \Nplease refrain from using them in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's ride this momentum \Nand go for Cliché #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gourmet scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have your fill of this \Nfresh bounty from the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have prepared a magic show \Nfor you after the Japanese ballad show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bottle of gasoline, \Nwarmed to body temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Cliché #3!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Bar Dead End
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interviewing people \Nat a bar on the outskirts of town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.09,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,229)}Bar Mistress Klaus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:08.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Do I ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman is my long separated \Nelder sister's friend's cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's the thieving bitch, \Nwho stole my lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this has become more like \Na daytime drama instead of suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:27.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, you she-pig! \NI'll turn you into cutlets and eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cliché #4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Makimura and Izumi have the advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is building up in a nice way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, this is just getting tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Maria, could it be that you've \Nbeen in the hot spring this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and so, I went back to our room \Nand I discovered something terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Maria?! \NQuit dragging it out and tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A body going missing \Nis as suspenseful as suspense gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. The case \Nis 5 seconds away from going cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder who hid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be the culprit, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he thinks he's interfering \Nwith my investigation by stirring things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, since it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys should be able to \Nfind some kind of definitive clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we've spotted this \Non the underside of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be a voice recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the scream we heard was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mystery is solved, my dear Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"M-My dear Watson"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Nagi's hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:12.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, do you know the culprit and the trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, wrong. Trick or treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick or treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me candy! Trick or treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been really tough \Nfor Halloween to catch on in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong kind of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have we suddenly come \Nto a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having the climax scene \Non an overhanging cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the biggest suspense dramas cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need Eiichiro Funakoshi \Nand we'd have it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I will explain how \Nthis incident was perpetrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This crime was actually not \Nperpetrated in that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you assume that it happened \Nat a completely different inn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a different room, it all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain it to us so we can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:14.99,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick #4
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the culprit met \Nwith the victim at some other inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on that occasion, \Nthe culprit recorded the victim's scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, h-hold on! It'll show, it'll show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit went to a different inn \Nwith a similar construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the culprit snuck her body \Ninto our room at that inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop! Be gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting the victim's scream on a timer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the culprit created the illusion \Nthat the crime had taken place there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We just heard a scream come \Nfrom that inn, didn't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a plot to create an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me, me! I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just the voice recorder, \Nit seems a bit forced...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest proof is \Non that videotape we saw first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,First of Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's recording properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything unusual about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you notice something \Nabout the scroll hanging there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,First of Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,115)}In Dire Distress \NHere Goes the Afro
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(439,72)}The Actual Room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, it's completely different \Nfrom the one in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit wasn't thorough
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and failed to pay attention \Nto the difference in the hanging scrolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also 4 other discrepancies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who find them all \Nwill have a chance to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've gotten this far, \Nyou know who the culprit is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I seem to recall there was \None person who came late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! And she brought \Nthat videotape, didn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, she said it came \Nby bike messenger or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sounding oddly defensive about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's actually the culprit, \Nthat just might explain everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:17:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku, I never imagined \Nthat you were the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it totally makes sense now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she is the least \Nsuspicious of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is exactly what makes her suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was brilliant detective work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that I'd be caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're right. Just \Nas you said, I'm the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is not Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! This is supposed to be my scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shock of this has woken me \Nfrom the tranquilizers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering this turn of events, \NI'm the only one who could be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be too normal and boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's hard to tell who's talking, \Nso would you mind stopping that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all forgotten to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That there's one more person \Nthat's incredibly suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That person is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person behind the Voice from Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss, isn't that too deus ex machina, \Nno matter how you look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know if our audience \Nwill be satisfied with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a suspense story \Nstarring me and produced by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will permit no one to complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea eliminating \Nmy presence halfway through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a corpse! Quit coming back \Nto life over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I can pretend \Nto stay dead the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! The script I pulled \Nan all-nighter to write is ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, \NI'll fall back to my last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, it's fan service time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing to do in autumn really is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to lounge in a hot spring \Nand admire the colored leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed! It's so soothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you all have a "Good \NJourney, Like a Dream", too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pure heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is the men's bath this small?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! It's caught! It's caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, that was the \N"Gluttony, Like a Dream",
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the deluxe 20 minute special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, they will be combating siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:59.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This Week's Butler Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Mysterious \NButler of Darkness No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat the butler Hayate Ayasaki \Nand make him one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make him one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Hayate Blaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to fight, \Nbring it on, Mysterious Butlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait, what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:51.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(412,294)}This Week's Butler Battle\N The End
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Waratte lun-lun-lun\NSmile lun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:58.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu naita hi mo\NLala-lun-lun-lulu even on a day I've cried
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:03.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawagu kaze ni yureru egao kokoro hareteku\NA smile wavers in the wind and clears my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou mo lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NToday again lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:18.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyou no shita de kimi to odoru kimagure na dansu\NA whimsical dance with you under the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:26.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanige-naku sashi-dasu te ni mitorete\NRiveted by the hand you've casually offered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:33.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugi no kotoba maigo ni natchau no\NMy next words become lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:37.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonabite tsutsumi-komu manazashi ni\NThe mature gaze that envelopes me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:43.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogari wasurete-yuku\NMakes me forget my bravado
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:49.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto furetete nemurenai yoru no nagai toki mo\NKeep that soft touch on long sleepless nights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:54.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume kara sameta bakari no hoho ni mo\NAnd on my cheek, just awakened from a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:56.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lun-lun-lun\NLun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:00.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu tsun to shita\NLala-lun-lun-lulu that hoity profile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:06.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokogao hora atto iu ma waratteru desho?\NLook, there's a smile there already, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:09.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora to lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NWith the sky lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:13.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ga fukasu kaze no naka\NIn a breeze of your making
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:20.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Odoru hidamari no dansu\NA dance in a sunny spot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.38,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ba-boom! Boing-oing-oing, \Nboing-oing-oing! I'm Nagi Sanzenin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm everybody's idol, Yukiji Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Miss Katsura?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold, Ayasaki. But more importantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When in the world is my character \Nsong going to be finished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, with Miss Katsura, \NI don't think the sales seem that promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.49,0:23:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pairing up with Tama on a character \Nsong would probably be about just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've certainly learned \Nto speak out, Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next guest will be the hamster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:02.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Miss, you used to \Ncall Sakuya "Big Sister Saku"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:18.81,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:03.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A thing of the unpleasant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:05.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never looked after li'l kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:07.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why ya still haven't \Ngrown outta bein' a kiddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.22,0:24:10.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me! If I had younger siblings,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:12.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I could look after them \Nway better than you, Saku!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.73,0:24:14.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,For real? Then prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:15.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.72,0:24:17.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:19.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do You Like Pretty Rich Big Sisters?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:20.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Hayate the Combat Butler \NDo You Like Pretty Rich Big Sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:24.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing the Wright brothers flew \Nwas the younger brother's mobile.
